title: Good Morning Football Podcast Episode 10
itunes:title: Good Morning Football Podcast Episode 10
description:
On the #GMFB Podcast this week: Nate recaps his weekend trip to LA (1:22); Is it possible to have a casual weekend trip in Vegas? (9:05); Peter talks about his weekend working the sidelines of a collegiate all-star game (13:23); The Atlanta Falcons and Matt Ryan playing in the Super Bowl (17:10); Do fans have “Patriots Fatigue?" (24:40); What makes a good Super Bowl matchup? (30:02); How does experience factor into the big game? (34:24); Chris Hogan, lacrosse & Patriots ability to get production from everywhere (37:58); The hosts present their Super Bowl Survival Tips (45:02); and Nate ends the show with a Blind Item Story (48:57).
